    "headline": "Ventas Declares Quarterly Dividend of $0.52 Per Common Share",
    "summary": "CHICAGO, May 13, 2026--Ventas, Inc. (NYSE: VTR) today announced that its Board of Directors has declared a quarterly dividend of $0.52 per common share. The dividend will be payable in cash on July 16, 2026, to stockholders of record as of the close of business on June 30, 2026.",
